content: I'm looking for some recommendations on performance air filters for my 2018 Ford Mustang GT. I recently modified my exhaust system and I'm looking to squeeze out some more power. By the way, I just participated in the "Turbocharged Tuesdays" auto racking event at the local racing track on June 14th, where I managed to achieve a personal best time of 12.8 seconds in the quarter-mile drag race.
